Jurgen Klopp will leave Borussia Dortmund at the end of the season . 
  The German confirmed in a press conference on Wednesday that he is to leave the club . 
  Klopp is favourite to replace Manuel Pellegrini at Manchester City . 
  The 47-year-old has also been linked with Liverpool and Arsenal . 
  Klopp said he believes Dortmund need a change next season . 
 